data.description: Welcome Home! Beautiful country home located in the heart of Needville, Tx.  Perfect location, simply enjoy the peace and quiet of country living. This Traditional Styled 2,261 sq foot country home has 4 bedroom 2.5 baths, open concept kitchen, freshly painted and new flooring, fully fenced back yard and large enough for a great big swimming pool, 12.8 x 8 shed in the back yard, retention pond is down the street from the house, propane connection on property, Great schools located very close to the home, and forgot to mention Needville is the home of our WORLD SERIES Little Leaguer's.  They placed #4 in the entire world!  This is a great opportunity to move out to the country. NO FLOODING HERE!
